dji.sdk.api.Camera

Class DJICameraProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.Camera.DJICameraProperty

  • public class DJICameraProperty
extends java.lang.Object

    Dji Camera Property Class

    This class is designed for holding the basic information or parameters about the Camera. The dji camera will provide fixed photo size and format. Developer could get the value by using the enum. Other information such as iso, white balance, will also include in this data structure.
    Version:
    V2.4.0
    Author:
    DJI Software
